{"_path":"/resident/r042","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"社區營造 - 街道遊戲場提案","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r042-01.jpeg","sequence":42,"category":"社區營造","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"社區營造-假日街道遊戲場提案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社區營造 - 假日街道遊戲場提案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"主旨-在-a7-重劃區建立假日街道遊戲場"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主旨 在 A7 重劃區建立假日街道遊戲場"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區是首購族的首選， 社區內年輕家族及幼童比例很高。 希望給兒童一個快樂的生活/遊戲環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區有許多街道 能於假日封街成為 步道區及遊戲場。 加上社區開放空間及統一的退縮綠帶區，能形成極佳的假日休閒遊戲環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望比照國外的城市假日封街做法如下圖"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-21.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-21.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區也有類似寬廣的行人道及行道樹！\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-22.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-22.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"辦法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望議員們能共同爭取桃園市社區營造獎勵經費, 建置移動式遊戲設施。 以有限經費打造高品質的遊戲環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同時希望附近科學園區的公司, A7 的建商 能贊助經費, 為 A7 重劃區提供優質的宜居環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請參考下面 國外的 街道遊戲場範例"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下午除了上輔導班, 也讓兒童能在此騎沒有交通風險的腳踏車。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-02.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-02.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"隨時來場街道棋藝競賽, 象棋, 圍棋 或五子棋 都不錯。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-03.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-03.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果一天的上課上班 有氣難消, 在此可以發洩一下。 打爆這個拳擊包。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-04.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-04.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"跳方塊也練習數字。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-05.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-05.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以十多人 一起打的桌球場地。 球拍還可現場借！\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-06.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-06.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把握每一分鐘, 隨時投個藍。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-07.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-07.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大人小孩全家一起玩的遊戲台。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r042-08.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r042-08.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上下學途中就在此能玩